From 4b826a8caa8cd2f38a9e5477ff47f510849455cf Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Aishwarya R <aisr@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Wed, 2 Jul 2025 16:05:27 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] UPSTREAM:DP:wifi: mac80211: Implement set_dscp_tid call
 back function to notify qos_map_set events from mac80211

Currently, ath12k follows fixed DSCP to TID mapping.Add support
for dynamic DSCP to TID mapping based on qos_map_set values from
mac80211.

Add support for TID offload mechanism when Hardware supports
IEEE80211_HW_SUPPORTS_DSCP_TID_MAP.

Implement set_dscp_tid call back function to notify driver upon
receiving qos_map_set events from mac80211 and update TID registers
accordingly.

Patch-dependency: none
Signed-off-by: Aishwarya R <aisr@qti.qualcomm.com>
---
